      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">This guide was assembled for those manufacturers that may not have
                the resources to maintain staff dedicated to evaluating potential investments. It is
                an overview of the primary methods used for evaluating investments in manufacturing
                technologies and is designed to minimize the amount of time and resources needed to
                understand them.</abstract>
